{"tid":2145751,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"迎合中國市場  高海寧、陳敏之大玩抖音","createTime":"2020-08-08T08:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T12:59:05.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"292f0829b7a30858deca51badac0103b9c673ab1","tid":2145751,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"TVB去年因反送中運動，經常被指報導偏頗，而被廣告商杯葛不在TVB刊登廣告，導致TVB收入銳減，甚至估計截至6月杪的中期業績虧損約2億9000萬港幣。為了迎合中國人和融入當地人的思維，TVB早前要求旗下藝人開設抖音帳號，而高海寧、陳敏之等也應公司要求，開始大玩抖音。<br />\n<br />\nTVB被廣告商離棄後，只能依靠北望神州，來幫助他們在中國14億人的市場分一杯羹。他們早前也被指為了迎合中國人和融入他們的思維，而要求旗下藝人開設抖音帳號，並要經常更新和分享，好好經營抖音，更表示若抖音擁有1萬追隨者，便會幫該藝人在抖音上取得認證。<br />\n<br />\n由於香港許多藝人已經習慣用面書、IG和微博分享日常生活，加上抖音需要將手機帳號轉成中國地區才能下載，也不能同時經營臉書和IG，所以不少藝人都對公司的舉動表示不滿。不過，也有一些藝人順應公司的要求，如高海寧、陳敏之、唐詩詠和江儀等，紛紛開始在抖音上拍影片，以開拓中國市場。"},{"pid":"c5b093dc39fda1046fd8e6b4f2e5f8d68e0c170b","tid":2145751,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media5.orientaldaily.com.my/storage/resize_cache/images/uploads/news-cover/2020/AUG_2020/20200808/douyin.jpg/50b3113cbe19f7ce58d12bf8e8c59527.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia5.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fstorage%2Fresize_cache%2Fimages%2Fuploads%2Fnews-cover%2F2020%2FAUG_2020%2F20200808%2Fdouyin.jpg%2F50b3113cbe19f7ce58d12bf8e8c59527.jpg&h=0af4d3bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media5.orientaldaily.com.my/images/uploads/news/2020/AUG_2020/20200808/zhangjingchun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia5.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fimages%2Fuploads%2Fnews%2F2020%2FAUG_2020%2F20200808%2Fzhangjingchun.jpg&h=b7af435c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media5.orientaldaily.com.my/images/uploads/news/2020/AUG_2020/20200808/jiangyi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia5.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fimages%2Fuploads%2Fnews%2F2020%2FAUG_2020%2F20200808%2Fjiangyi.jpg&h=1a53d32d&s={S